data.name: FLUIDS TRANSFER SPIKE
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Acrylnitril-Butadien-Styrol (ABS) Body/Spikes
- Polypropylene (PP) Connector and Cap

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Natural and white color

## PERFORMANCE
- Strong and Sharp Tips
- Soft and anti-slip Surface colored Wings
- Minimum Dead Space
